TITLE: Removing Cookies for Specific URLs in VCL
DESCRIPTION: This VCL snippet demonstrates how to remove the cookie header for all requests to the '/images' directory. It uses a regular expression to match the URL and then unsets the cookie header if there's a match.
SOURCE: https://github.com/varnishcache/varnish-cache/blob/master/doc/sphinx/users-guide/vcl-example-manipulating-headers.rst#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: vcl
CODE:
```
sub vcl_recv {
  if (req.url ~ "^/images") {
    unset req.http.cookie;
  }
}
```

