TITLE: Resolving Backend Connections in VCL
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to explicitly resolve a backend connection in VCL using the .resolve() method. This is useful when the resolution outcome is needed within VCL, such as in server sharding scenarios.
SOURCE: https://github.com/varnishcache/varnish-cache/blob/master/doc/sphinx/users-guide/vcl-backends.rst#2025-04-17_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: vcl
CODE:
```
