TITLE: Basic URL-based Backend Selection in VCL
DESCRIPTION: A simple VCL configuration that demonstrates how to route traffic to different backend servers based on URL patterns. This example routes requests with URLs starting with '/wiki' to a wiki_server backend, while all other requests go to a wordpress_server backend.
