TITLE: Extended CHERI Pointer Capabilities Example in C
DESCRIPTION: Shows detailed CHERI pointer capabilities including bounds setting and permission inspection using printf formatting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/varnishcache/varnish-cache/blob/master/doc/sphinx/phk/cheri4.rst#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: c
CODE:
