TITLE: Displaying HTTP/2 SETTINGS_MAX_CONCURRENT_STREAMS Specification
DESCRIPTION: RFC7540 specification excerpt showing the SETTINGS_MAX_CONCURRENT_STREAMS parameter (0x3) that defines stream limits. The specification indicates there is no initial limit, creating a DoS vulnerability.
